{"tid":1773703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度強姦案受害人往法庭途中遭疑犯縱火 搶救不治","createTime":"2019-12-07T16:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T23:26:54.000Z","uid":133680,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"25d782fdbedeb5e223c03e489ad4d46737cb1a7d","tid":1773703,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=372564&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372564%26refer%3D&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=9cab6e4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D372564%26refer%3D&h=3ee01098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=372564&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n查看<br />\nnow 新聞 - 24小時直播<br />\nPCCW Media Limited<br />\n<br />\n兩岸國際<br />\n<br />\n印度強姦案受害人往法庭途中遭疑犯縱火 搶救不治<br />\n7小時前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】印度一名強姦案受害人，日前前往法庭途中，遭到案中疑犯等人放火襲擊，經搶救一日多後死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事發在周四，住在北方邦的23歲受害人，準備坐火車前往法院，為案件作證，但途中遭到五名男子襲擊，又向她身上放火，導致她身體有九成半被燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者說受害人大約走了一公里路求救，受害人隨後轉送到新德里救治，但延至周五不治。院方表示受害人吸入大量有毒氣體，氣管嚴重燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n事件在印度全國引起公憤，警方事後拘捕五名男子，其中兩人是強姦案疑犯，受害者家屬認為，當局應該將疑犯吊死或槍斃。<br />\n<br />\n日前印度警方開槍擊斃四名涉嫌姦殺女獸醫的疑犯，大批民眾上街慶祝，讚揚警方為死者伸張正義。"},{"pid":"2f3b38d97d18fa34fc937de93357101416012a9a","tid":1773703,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T16:25:22.000Z","msg":"個受害人係低種姓定untouchable？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b2caa113d8536c11a24227801f081e2756d444","tid":1773703,"uid":311583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /